high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the egg in the right side of the sink.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave above the stove.
Place the egg in the microwave and shut the door.
Turn right and walk forward and take a right past the table and then turn to the right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the egg on the kitchen table.
Turn right and step forward, then turn left and step forward and turn to the right to face the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave beside the first egg.
anns.task_desc: To gather two eggs and place them in the microwave.

high_descs: Go right and then turn left to face the sink.
Pick the egg up from the sink.
Go to the right and face the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave and shut the door.
Go right and then right again and turn to face the salt shaker on the table.
Pick the egg up from the table.
Go right and then left and turn to the right to face the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put two eggs in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn left at the sink, and face it.
Pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn to the right and walk to the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
Turn right, walk around the table, and walk up to it.
Pick up the egg in front of the tomato on the table.
Walk back to the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place two eggs in a microwave.
